column5: About times people have started staying indoors when many countries are under complete lock down since weeks now. I don't know it feels like we're falling behind

I ask myself if that would piss me off, if not I'll go ahead and ask.
Everyone's equally anxious.
I think Messi's dribbling is pretty accurate in Fifa 19 you just gotta have to understand it he'd easily past any player as compared to other dribblers in the game .
Plus traffic signals every 500m kills you from within.
